These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: june, may, august, april, december, october, july
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, biathlon, cycling, parkour, skiing, volleyball
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in july##2
 2. the person who's birthday is in may is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person who's sport is parkour##2
 5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 6. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 7. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
 8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
10. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
11. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Birthday   | april | june | july | may    | august | december   | october    |
| Sport         | skiing  | baseball   | cycling | badminton | biathlon   | volleyball | parkour |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
There 7 different types of food: apple, cauliflower, grapefruit, grapes, lettuce, pomegranate, pumpkin
House: palace, gothic-revival, futuristic, ranch-style, colonial, wooden, victorian
1. the wooden house is on the far left##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is between the person eating pomegranate and the wooden house##2
3. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the palace house##1
4. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the futuristic house##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is in the middle##1
6. the colonial house is on the left of the palace house##1
7. the victorian house is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
8. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
9. the person eating grapes is on the right of the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Food          | lettuce | grapefruit | pomegranate | cauliflower | pumpkin | apple      | grapes  |
| House   | wooden | ranch-style  | victorian     | futuristic     | colonial  | palace | gothic-revival |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
7 different games are played: whist, snooker, bridge, chess, scrabble, monopoly, billiard
7 different pets are kept: fish, goat, hamster, pony, rabbit, rat, turtle
 1. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 2. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 3. the owner of the rabbit is the person playing billiard##1
 4. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 5. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 6. the person playing chess is the owner of the pony##1
 7. the person playing whist is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 8. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the turtle and the person playing chess##2
 9. the person playing whist is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
10. the person playing snooker is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Game   | billiard | scrabble | whist | snooker   | chess | bridge | monopoly |
| Pet           | rabbit | rat     | goat     | hamster | pony   | fish   | turtle    |

