.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: funk, disco, indie, jazz, trance, pop, metal
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, chinese, malaysian, mexican, nigerian, pakistani, polish
 1. the fan of metal is on the left of the malaysian##1
 2. the fan of trance is on the right of the nigerian##1
 3. the pakistani is on the right of the mexican##1
 4. the fan of trance is on the right of the nigerian##1
 5. the australian is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 6. the mexican is between the fan of indie and the pakistani##2
 7. the fan of funk is in the middle##1
 8. the mexican is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
 9. the fan of disco is the chinese##1
10. the australian is the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Music-Genre      | indie    | trance  | jazz  | funk  | metal      | pop       | disco |
| Nationality   | nigerian | mexican | pakistani | polish | australian | malaysian | chinese  |

