.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: classical, disco, folk, house, metal, punk, rock
7 different games are played: billiard, poker, canasta, go, monopoly, snooker, mah-jongg
1. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person playing monopoly is the fan of disco##1
3. the person playing billiard is between the fan of rock and the fan of classical##2
4. the fan of punk is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
5. the person playing billiard is in the middle##1
6. the person playing snooker is on the left of the fan of classical##1
7. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
8. the person playing poker is the fan of house##1
9. the fan of metal is the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | house      | metal | classical | folk | rock      | disco      | punk |
| Game     | poker | snooker | mah-jongg       | billiard | canasta | monopoly | go |

