.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, fanta, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, lemonade, milk
House: futuristic, art-deco, gothic-revival, craftsman, victorian, colonial, farmhouse
 1. the colonial house is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
 3. the art-deco house is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking fanta is between the victorian house and the farmhouse house##2
 5. the futuristic house is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the futuristic house##1
 7. the craftsman house is the person drinking coffee##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is the victorian house##1
 9. the gothic-revival house is between the victorian house and the person drinking iced-tea##2
10. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Beverage   | coffee | cola    | hot-chocolate | fanta   | lemonade | milk    | iced-tea |
| House      | craftsman | futuristic | farmhouse    | art-deco | victorian    | gothic-revival | colonial  |

