.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-8::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, hot-chocolate, juice, lemonade, mirinda, water
There are 7 different nationalities: polish, russian, nigerian, malaysian, chinese, argentine, german
 1. the chinese is on the left of the malaysian##1
 2. the polish is on the left of the nigerian##1
 3. the argentine is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 5. the chinese is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking water##2
 7. the russian is on the right of the argentine##1
 8. the polish is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 9. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
10. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking water and the person drinking cola##2
11. the chinese is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate  | lemonade   | cola         | fanta     | water              | mirinda    | juice     |
| Nationality        | argentine | russian | chinese | malaysian | german | polish | nigerian |

