.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-9::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: skateboarding, golf, rugby, parkour, climbing, tennis, lacrosse
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, quad-bike, skateboard, taxi, tram, trike
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person driving the tram##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person driving the trike and the person driving the taxi##2
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
5. the person driving the bus is in the middle##1
6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
7. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
8. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
9. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
| Sport   | golf | parkour     | tennis | climbing | rugby | lacrosse  | skateboarding |
| Transport     | quad-bike | skateboard | taxi   | bus     | trike    | motorbike | tram   |

