.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-10::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, cola, fanta, milk, mirinda, tea
7 different games are played: scrabble, canasta, domino, backgammon, monopoly, billiard, mah-jongg
1. the person playing billiard is the person drinking cola##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person playing domino is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person playing billiard is between the person playing backgammon and the person playing canasta##2
5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing domino##1
6. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
8. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking milk and the person playing billiard##2
9. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | coffee  | 7up       | tea         | milk         | fanta   | cola        | mirinda |
| Game      | mah-jongg | domino | scrabble | monopoly | canasta | billiard | backgammon  |

