.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-11::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: cooking, hiking, puzzles, reading, rock-climbing, singing, woodworking
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, bluemaster, montecristo, aristoff, havana, blend, alhambra
1. the alhambra-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in the middle##1
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
5. the prince-smoker is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
6. the person who's hobby is reading is between the havana-smoker and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
7. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
9. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |       2       |     3      |       4       |    5    |     6      |       7       |
| Hobby   | woodworking | singing       | puzzles    | rock-climbing | reading | hiking     | cooking       |
| Cigar   | bluemaster    | aristoff | blend | havana        | montecristo | prince | alhambra |

