 4. the victorian house is between the cape-cod house and the tower house##2
 5. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of house##1
 6. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 7. the cottage house is on the far right##1
 8. the cottage house is the fan of punk##1
 9. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
10. the fan of pop is the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3   |   4   |    5    |   6    |   7    |
| House   | gothic-revival | modern | farmhouse  | tower   | victorian | cape-cod | cottage |
| Music-Genre   | pop     | salsa       | disco | house | reggae  | folk   | punk   |

