 5. the person who growsiris is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 7. the person who growsbegonia is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 8. the person who growslily is the person who growslily##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
10. the person who growslily is on the left of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2    |     3     |       4       |      5      |    6     |    7     |
| Beverage   | fanta       | mirinda | milk      | hot-chocolate | water       | iced-tea | lemonade |
