.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-20::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: horror, epic, western, sports, superhero, comedy, family
The people have 7 different jobs:  accountant, architect, electrician, engineer, mechanic, project-manager, software-developer
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the electrician##1
2. the mechanic is in the middle##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching western movies is between the person watching sports movies and the accountant##2
5. the electrician is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
6. the project-manager is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
7. the mechanic is on the right of the engineer##1
8. the software-developer is between the person watching family movies and the project-manager##2
9. the person watching family movies is on the right of the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |         5          |        6        |     7      |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | epic    | horror | family | sports              | western      | superhero    |
| Job    | architect | electrician | engineer  | mechanic   | software-developer | project-manager | accountant |

 